      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANGAR POLLY (6) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this trip which boasts two wins. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (42.47) in a Grade 5, finishing a 7 length fourth. Looks the one to beat with even luck. GRAMERCY GARRY (8) broke a string of placings finishing in the money three on end before a last start seventh (42.66) at Wentworth Park. Has never been out of the money in five starts this course and distance. Deserves plenty of respect. RAYMAR SHAME (2) clocked a useful 29.83 when placed over 520m at Wentworth Park last start in a Grade 5. In form and looks a leading player again. ALL CHAMPAGNE (3) picked up a minor cheque in close finish most recently - in the mix again.",
